%N A395618 Decimal expansion of Sum_{k>=1} H(k)/((k+1)^2*2^k), where H(k) = A001008(k)/A002805(k) is the k-th harmonic number.
%H A395618 Michael I. Shamos, <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220206102634/https://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.366.9997&amp;rep=rep1&amp;type=pdf">Shamos's Catalog of the Real Numbers</a>, 2011.
