%H A395618 <a href="/index/Ha#harmonic">Index entries for sequences related to harmonic numbers</a>.
%F A395618 Equals zeta(3)/4 - log(2)^3/3.
%F A395618 Equals Integral_{x=0..1} log(1+x)^2/(x*(x+1)) dx = Integral_{x=1..2} log(x)^2/(x*(x-1)) dx (Shamos, 2011, p. 253).
